{"pid":"6acb7363b54cebc7706db3c5b81c01ae458f262a","tid":384813,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都好一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人應該冇咩顧忌幾舒服?</blockquote><br />\n從來都係做返自己<br />\n唔會講遺背自己良心既野<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界太多虛偽既人<br />\n少我一個唔少<br />\n朋友同學同事, 一向夾到就夾<br />\n夾唔到亦唔會強求<br />\n反而我做返真正既自己係唔少地方都識到朋友<br />\n唔怕無朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我相信咁樣一定係識到好多真正志同道合嘅朋友<br />\n但你會點應對D虛偽嘅人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我自己玩心理學10幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個係人邊個係鬼我好快就會睇穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果堆人慢慢就會過濾左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真觀察力很強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇D tips分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ab977a81c014fa4dd306815793b960407c0a43","tid":384813,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>現實中係一個樂觀無煩惱咩事都睇得好開既人<br />\n連登既我不斷叫春放負除低平時戴住既面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔想同身邊識既人講<br />\n唯有上連登講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗起一首歌個MV- 你不是真正的快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戴住面具做人真係好攰呢.. <br />\n做一個樂觀嘅人好多時會吸引身邊人嚟同你放負、希望你開解佢，<br />\n但其實自己都好負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打情況係咪咁呀，所以唔想同身邊人講?</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實自己本身都係鐘意做聆聽者/安慰者既角色<br />\n總係會好唔習慣放負俾其他人<br />\n有時都會既<br />\n但多數講一次或者輕描淡寫咁講下就算<br />\n講得多好驚人地會煩<br />\n同埋覺得始終佢唔係我唔會明我點諗<br />\n有時啲負面既感覺要我講一時三刻都唔知點講好<br />\n所以就寧願收埋唔講算數"},{"pid":"82d7e92c8333e40591e715d33674d4a7c6f313a3","tid":384813,"uid":112784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"其實只係將平日facebook 既自己搬過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為平時facebook唔會有fd理"},{"pid":"dbb1e318b6d61f08318763fa11600739d025e555","tid":384813,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇咩分別 兩邊都唔係點講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n是咪少說話多做事嘅人?"},{"pid":"65fd5950c581afc7809f6fd6fe48eaa2e31b384b","tid":384813,"uid":112784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登：同人講到政治打機哲學同埋睇人仆街<br />\n<br />\n現實：講食咩，有咩事發生，邊個生日等普通野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c320f76322c519f30a6635f9044ca329503beb0","tid":384813,"uid":112784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KfBDwZZUF34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKfBDwZZUF34&d=ZoqK%2FXN3%2BWtxG0VrodnihZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fe24b2bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KfBDwZZUF34</a><br />\n<br />\n匿名嘅好處"},{"pid":"a8ee96c23e92d3a55f2b5af611a944dc33cd422f","tid":384813,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都好一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人應該冇咩顧忌幾舒服?</blockquote><br />\n從來都係做返自己<br />\n唔會講遺背自己良心既野<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界太多虛偽既人<br />\n少我一個唔少<br />\n朋友同學同事, 一向夾到就夾<br />\n夾唔到亦唔會強求<br />\n反而我做返真正既自己係唔少地方都識到朋友<br />\n唔怕無朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我相信咁樣一定係識到好多真正志同道合嘅朋友<br />\n但你會點應對D虛偽嘅人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我自己玩心理學10幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個係人邊個係鬼我好快就會睇穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果堆人慢慢就會過濾左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真觀察力很強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇D tips分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無例子唔識得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過例如有活動咁樣先算<br />\n經過一晚相處對答你都一定會留意到啲野<br />\n我都係一樣, 只不過可能比你更多<br />\n仲要有背後既理由支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5eff260defe730ba47cbf7b8964917d6370ecf3","tid":384813,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登：同人講到政治打機哲學同埋睇人仆街<br />\n<br />\n現實：講食咩，有咩事發生，邊個生日等普通野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好似一個好有抱負嘅人但現實中冇機會俾你表達自己真正關心嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇試過係自己圈子開呢D topic?</blockquote><br />\n絕大多數都唔係呢d人<br />\n因為小弟有比較特別嘅社交圈子<br />\n差唔多年齡個d基本上都唔會講呢d<br />\n然後比我大個d(有d做得我老竇)好少會傾呢d因為自己未有本錢<br />\n2.玩親嘅game通常都係得自己鍾意，所以通常都會搵其他谷，畢竟喜好冇得迫，得自己鍾意咪繼續<br />\n<br />\n3.個人經歷+性格所以唔會開topic"},{"pid":"d3bac4f7a04